<template><div><h1 id="parse-passwd" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#parse-passwd" aria-hidden="true">#</a> parse-passwd <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/parse-passwd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/v/parse-passwd.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM version"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://npmjs.org/package/parse-passwd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/dm/parse-passwd.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM downloads"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://travis-ci.org/doowb/parse-passwd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/travis/doowb/parse-passwd.svg?style=flat&amp;label=Travis" alt="Linux Build Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://ci.appveyor.com/project/doowb/parse-passwd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/appveyor/ci/doowb/parse-passwd.svg?style=flat&amp;label=AppVeyor" alt="Windows Build Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h1>
<blockquote>
<p>Parse a passwd file into a list of users.</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="install" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#install" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Install</h2>
<p>Install with <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">npm<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>:</p>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> --save parse-passwd
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="usage" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#usage" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Usage</h2>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">var</span> parse <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">require</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'parse-passwd'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="api" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#api" aria-hidden="true">#</a> API</h2>
<p><strong>Example</strong></p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token comment">// assuming '/etc/passwd' contains:</span>
<span class="token comment">// doowb:*:123:123:Brian Woodward:/Users/doowb:/bin/bash</span>
console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">parse</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>fs<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">readFileSync</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'/etc/passwd'</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">'utf8'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

<span class="token comment">//=> [</span>
<span class="token comment">//=>   {</span>
<span class="token comment">//=>     username: 'doowb',</span>
<span class="token comment">//=>     password: '*',</span>
<span class="token comment">//=>     uid: '123',</span>
<span class="token comment">//=>     gid: '123',</span>
<span class="token comment">//=>     gecos: 'Brian Woodward',</span>
<span class="token comment">//=>     homedir: '/Users/doowb',</span>
<span class="token comment">//=>     shell: '/bin/bash'</span>
<span class="token comment">//=>   }</span>
<span class="token comment">//=> ]</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>Params</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><code v-pre>content</code> <strong>{String}</strong>: Content of a passwd file to parse.</li>
<li><code v-pre>returns</code> <strong>{Array}</strong>: Array of user objects parsed from the content.</li>
</ul>
